hopobject.body: I came here to work medicoremediesindia.net "The interpretation is that we must control CO2, but we must put in place programs with real resources walking the talk to develop these technologies," Moniz said. Obama recently directed the Environmental Protection Agency to develop regulations limiting the carbon output of existing coal plants, but the industry is upset because of the prohibitive costs of retro-fitting old plants with carbon sequestering technology.
